RWS Says Ottway Named CEO; Trading ‘In Line’ With Forecasts

-- B y   D a v i d   A l t a n e r
-- 
2011-10-12T06:13:29Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-12/rws-says-ottway-named-ceo-trading-in-line-with-forecasts.html
RWS Holdings Plc (RWS)  said Liz Lucas will
retire as chief executive officer of its translation unit.
Reinhard Ottway has been named as group chief executive,
effective Jan. 1, the company said.  Group trading is “in line” with forecasts, the company
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
